OL,3,CSecond horse dies at Cheltenham
OL,4,CFestival 2026: HMS Seahorse 'could not
OL,5,Cbe saved'
OL,7,FA second horse has been put down after
OL,8,Fa race at Cheltenham Festival 2026.
OL,10,FHMS Seahorse sustained an injury when
OL,11,Ffalling at the final hurdle of the
OL,12,Fthird race of the day.
OL,14,FThe horse was attended to by vets but
OL,15,FCheltenham racecourse has confirmed it
OL,16,Fcould not be saved.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
