OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773324683
OL,3,CSecond horse dies at Cheltenham
OL,4,CFestival 2026: HMS Seahorse 'could not
OL,5,Cbe saved'
OL,7,FA spokesperson at the festival said:
OL,8,F"HMS Seahorse was immediately attended
OL,9,Fto by a team of expert vets during our
OL,10,Fthird race of the day, but sadly
OL,11,Fsustained an injury when falling at
OL,12,Fthe final hurdle and could not be
OL,13,Fsaved. Our heartfelt condolences are
OL,14,Fwith connections."
OL,16,FReferring to Hansard, who died on day
OL,17,Fone Cheltenham racecourse said: "While
OL,18,Frunning on the flat in the second race
OL,19,Fof the day, Hansard sustained a fatal
OL,20,Finjury.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
